.jpg","thumbnail_small":"","thumbnail_medium":"","thumbnail_full":"https://global.ariseplay.com/amg/www.thisdaylive.com/uploads/tinubu-2.jpg","excerpt":"","author":{"id":89715,"slug":"elumoye","name":"Deji Elumoye"},"category":{"id":7588,"slug":"breaking","name":"Breaking","count":20218},"url":"/index.php/2024/03/13/tinubu-orders-immediate-reopening-of-borders-with-niger"},{"title":"Mali, Burkina Faso Send ‘Formal Notice’ of Withdrawal from ECOWAS","slug":"mali-burkina-faso-send-formal-notice-of-withdrawal-from-ecowas","date":"2024-01-31T04:21:51","agoDate":"2 months ago","thumbnail":"https://global.ariseplay.com/amg/www.thisdaylive.com/uploads/ECOWAS-800x450.jpeg","thumbnail_small":"https://global.ariseplay.com/amg/www.thisdaylive.com/uploads/ECOWAS-150x150.jpeg","thumbnail_medium":"https://global.ariseplay.com/amg/www.thisdaylive.com/uploads/ECOWAS-800x450.jpeg","thumbnail_full":"https://global.ariseplay.com/amg/www.thisdaylive.com/uploads/ECOWAS.jpeg","excerpt":"","author":{"id":89847,"slug":"addeh","name":"Emmanuel Addeh"},"category":{"id":7588,"slug":"breaking","name":"Breaking","count":20218},"url":"/index.php/2024/01/31/mali-burkina-faso-send-formal-notice-of-withdrawal-from-ecowas"},{"title":"Mali, Burkina Faso, Niger Quit ECOWAS, Say regional bloc Under Foreign Control","slug":"mali-burkina-faso-niger-quit-ecowas-say-regional-bloc-under-foreign-control","date":"2024-01-29T03:08:19","agoDate":"2 months ago","thumbnail":"https://global.ariseplay.com/amg/www.thisdaylive.com/uploads/ECOWAS-800x450.jpeg","thumbnail_small":"https://global.ariseplay.com/amg/www.thisdaylive.com/uploads/ECOWAS-150x150.jpeg","thumbnail_medium":"https://global.ariseplay.com/amg/www.thisdaylive.com/uploads/ECOWAS-800x450.jpeg","thumbnail_full":"https://global.ariseplay.com/amg/www.thisdaylive.com/uploads/ECOWAS.jpeg","excerpt":"","author":{"id":89847,"slug":"addeh","name":"Emmanuel Addeh"},"category":{"id":7588,"slug":"breaking","name":"Breaking","count":20218},"url":"/index.php/2024/0